  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Redis缓存架构的Git演进图。主干是main分支，最开始有个初始化提交a。然后从main分出两个特性分支feature_1和feature_2，feature_1要在左边，feature_2在右边，视觉上分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit a",
        "branch feature_1",
        "branch feature_2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，feature_1的order设为0，feature_2的order设为2，这样中间留空一格，视觉上更清爽。那feature_1上的开发节奏怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature_1 order:0",
        "feature_2 order:2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "feature_1先做提交f，然后切回main做提交b——这是线上热修复。接着再切回feature_1继续开发提交g。feature_2那边相对独立，第一次切过去的时候做提交u。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout feature_1",
        "commit f",
        "checkout main",
        "commit b",
        "commit g",
        "checkout feature_2",
        "commit u"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，主干有了a和b两个提交，feature_1上有f和g，feature_2上有了u。接下来feature_1和feature_2还有后续提交吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main: a,b",
        "feature_1: f,g",
        "feature_2: u"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有的，两边要交替推进体现并行开发。feature_1再做提交h，feature_2跟进提交v。最后都开发完了，main分支先后合并feature_1和feature_2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit h",
        "commit v",
        "merge feature_1",
        "merge feature_2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我梳理一下流程：从feature_1切到feature_2做v之前，需要先checkout feature_2对吧？而且合并顺序是先feature_1后feature_2，这样主干最终包含所有特性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout feature_2",
        "merge feature_1",
        "merge feature_2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，顺序别搞错。feature_1的h是在第二次切回feature_1时做的，然后才切到feature_2做v。合并顺序也确认是先1后2。",
      "elements_involved": [
